@startuml seq_26_configure_community
title Sequence Diagram: UC-26 Configure Community

actor Moderator
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Community Controller" as Controller
participant "Community Service" as Service
participant "Cloudinary" as Cloudinary
participant "Community Repo" as Repo

Moderator -> Frontend: Update settings & media, then Save
Frontend -> Controller: PUT /api/communities/{id}/settings (multipart form)
Controller -> Service: Update Community Settings
Service -> Repo: Verify ownership or moderator access
Repo --> Service: Access confirmed

alt New avatar or banner uploaded
    Service -> Cloudinary: Upload new image stream
    Cloudinary --> Service: Return Media URLs & IDs
end

Service -> Repo: Update Community record in DB
Repo --> Service: Record updated
Service --> Controller: Saved Settings Data
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> Moderator: Show success message & refresh UI
@enduml